《仙乐传说》所获媒体评价普遍积极。美版发行头两周销量超过10万<ref name="Two Weeks">{{cite web|last=Preziotte |first=Mathew |title=July 2004 Sales Figures for America |publisher=Nintelligent Network |date=2004-08-16 |url=http://www.nintelligent.net/news2063.php |accessdate=2012-05-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050222213823/http://www.nintelligent.net/news2063.php |archivedate=2005-02-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。南梦宫在2007年12月宣布，GameCube版全球销量超过95.3万，PlayStation 2移植版日本销量达到48.6万<ref name="10 million">{{cite web| title=''Tales'' series exceeds 10 million copies| publisher=[[Namco_Bandai_Games|Namco Bandai Games]]| date=December 11, 2007| format=pdf| language=ja| url=http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/corporate/press/pdf/53-026.pdf| accessdate=2012-05-01| archive-date=2014-12-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141204225401/http://www.bandainamcogames.co.jp/corporate/press/pdf/53-026.pdf| dead-url=no}}</ref>。2005年推出的PlayStation 2廉价版到2006年末时售出近5万<ref name="EBsales">{{Cite book |publisher=[[Enterbrain|Enterbrain]] |year=2007 |isbn=978-4-7577-3577-4 |location=Tokyo |page=387 |id={{NDL|21240454}} |language=ja |title=ファミ通ゲーム白書2007 |chapter=2006年ゲームソフト年間売上TOP500 |url=http://geimin.net/da/db/2006_ne_fa/index.php |access-date=2015-08-31 |archive-date=2015-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626214525/http://geimin.net/da/db/2006_ne_fa/index.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏各版全球累计销量在2008年达160万，是当时最畅销的传说作品<ref name="IWinterview">{{cite web|url=http://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/20080414/tov1.htm |title=特別インタビュー Xbox 360「テイルズ オブ ヴェスペリア」（前編） |publisher=Impress Watch |date=2008-04-14 |accessdate=2012-11-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711135219/http://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/20080414/tov1.htm |archivedate=2014-07-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《仙乐传说》登上多项榜单。游戏是[[日本游戏大奖|日本游戏大奖]]2003优秀奖获奖作品之一<ref name="JGA">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/67uyVGUu7?url=http://awards.cesa.or.jp/2004/english/prizelist/ |archivedate=2012-05-25 |url=http://awards.cesa.or.jp/2004/english/prizelist/ |title=Japan Game Awards 2003–2004 |publisher=[[Computer_Entertainment_Supplier's_Association|Computer Entertainment Supplier's Association]] |accessdate=2012-05-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。在《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》2009年1月刊中，游戏入选“25款最佳GameCube游戏”并获第24名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2009/09/22/feature-gamecube-top-25-list.aspx |title=GameCube Top 25 |author=Ben Reeves |work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |date=2009-09-22 |accessdate=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2012-10-07 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BEJawFvE?url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2009/09/22/feature-gamecube-top-25-list.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》的“200款史上最佳任天堂游戏”榜单中，《仙乐传说》位居第107位<ref>{{cite journal|title=NP Top 200 |journal=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] |volume=200 | date = 2006-02 |page=63}}</ref>。在[[IGN|IGN]]的百佳游戏读者票选中，游戏位居第75名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://top100.ign.com/2008/ign_top_game_75.html |title=IGN Top 100 Games 2008 Reader's Choice - 75: Tales of Symphonia |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |accessdate=2010-08-21 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BEJccGuy?url=http://top100.ign.com/2008/ign_top_game_75.html |archive-date=2012-10-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>；而在GameSpot的类似读者投票中，游戏位居第81位<ref>{{cite web|title=10-Year Anniversary Contest — The 10 Best Games Ever |url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/top10 |publisher=[[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]] |accessdate=2006-10-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716111618/http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/top10 |archivedate=2015-07-16 }}</ref>。

评论对游戏的卡通动画风格和即时战斗系统表示称赞。[[1UP.com|1UP]]、[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]、[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]、IGN和[[X-Play|X-Play]]称赞了作品精细的场景，GameSpy还提到游戏的60帧画面很稳定<ref name="GameSpot review">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tales-of-symphonia-review/1900-6102021/ |title=GameSpot ''Tales of Symphonia'' review |last=Massimilla |first=Bethany |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2004-07-06 |accessdate=2012-05-15 |archive-date=2020-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425041948/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tales-of-symphonia-review/1900-6102021/ }}</ref><ref name="1UP review">{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/reviews/tales-of-symphonia |title=1UP ''Tales of Symphonia'' review |last=Nutt |first=Christian |date=2004-08-10 |publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |accessdate=2012-05-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104214635/http://www.1up.com/reviews/tales-of-symphonia |archivedate=2013-11-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="GameSpy review" /><ref name="IGN review" /><ref name="XPlay review">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060104173909/http://www.g4tv.com/xplay/features/47952/Tales_of_Symphonia_Review.html |url=http://www.g4tv.com/xplay/features/47952/Tales_of_Symphonia_Review.html |title=X-Play ''Tales of Symphonia'' review |date=2004-09-08 |publisher=[[X-Play|X-Play]] |archivedate=2006-01-04 |accessdate=2012-05-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。GameSpy称游戏战斗系统“畅快扼要”，X-Play则表示其易上手、有吸引非RPG玩家的潜力<ref name="GameSpy review" /><ref name="XPlay review" />。游戏剧情和声音获评消极。[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]、GameSpot、GameSpy、IGN和X-Play表示批评情节老生常谈、难以抓人<ref name="GameSpot review" /><ref name="IGN review" /><ref name="GameSpy review" /><ref name="Eurogamer review">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/r_TalesOfSymphonia_GC |title=Eurogamer ''Tales Of Symphonia'' Review |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2004-11-02 |first=Rob |last=Fahey |accessdate=2012-05-15 |archive-date=2012-10-07 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BEJZYf3b?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/r_TalesOfSymphonia_GC |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="XPlay review" />。评论称游戏音乐和英语配音达标。此外GameSpy和X-Play称角色见的互动很迷人<ref name="GameSpy review" /><ref name="XPlay review" />。

